data.description: SOLAR PANELS ARE OWNED AND WILL BE PAID IN FULL BY THE SELLER AT CLOSING. Nestled in a picturesque cul-de-sac this Woodland Hills residence is in proximity to top-rated schools, a vibrant shopping scene, diverse dining options, The Commons, and the lively Warner Center entertainment district. This immaculately updated 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 1792 sqft. home on an expansive 7600+ sqft. lot beckons with a captivating blend of comfort, functionality, and aesthetic appeal for the family of today. The property boasts a sparkling pool, making it the perfect haven for those seeking a quintessential California lifestyle. The inviting open floor plan unfolds upon entry, revealing a stunning expanded kitchen designed for culinary enthusiasts and home chefs. Seamlessly adjoining this gourmet kitchen is a spacious living room replete with built-ins and a dining area that fosters memorable gatherings, all graced by the elegance of newer hardwood floors. The master bedroom showcases an upgraded ensuite bath, offering a private retreat within the home. The remaining bedrooms are generously appointed for comfort. Appreciate the beauty of indoor-outdoor living with two sliders leading to a spacious, thoughtfully hardscaped backyard to accommodate a luxurious swimmer's pool. This meticulously maintained property features copper plumbing, a newer roof and insulation, a newer electrical panel and HVAC system, Solar panels, newer windows, and plantation shutters, ensuring it is aesthetically pleasing and well-equipped for modern living. In addition to the charms of the home itself, its location is a noteworthy feature.
